**Topic** : Why do we need Docker?

![](data:image/png;base64,)

**Article Source** :

- [Why Docker](https://www.docker.com/why-docker/)
- [What Is Docker And Why Do We Need It?](https://medium.com/codex/what-is-docker-and-why-do-we-need-it-7dedc616366e)
- Docker Hub : [https://hub.docker.com/](https://hub.docker.com/)

**TL;DR** :

Docker simplifies and accelerates application development and deployment by packaging applications and their dependencies into isolated, portable containers. This approach allows developers to deliver software faster, maintain consistent environments across different stages of development, and improve resource utilization.
